channel.title: Post Your OWN ORIGINAL Sample Packs Here!
channel.description: The new Auxy update includes the feature where you can import WAVE files into the app as samples, as you probably know. So if you have any cool or interesting samples you want to share, post a link in this thread! To get things started, here's a little sample pack I made myself: [8-Bit Sound Pack](https://drive.google.com/open?id=16fUv2ABu6YVBPcxC6oraMujvPYFs6zI2)
